{{wikipediapar|Tic tac toe}}
==English==
===Noun===
'''[[tic]] [[tac]] [[toe]]''' (''uncountable'')
# A children's [[game]] in which opponents take turns adding an "X" or "O" to empty spaces in a three by three grid, with the winner being the first to place three of their mark in a straight line.

